description: Kyle never really noticed how he felt about Kip his roommate, until Kip started dating another guy. Kyle was surprised by his jealousy. He kept it to himself until Kip and his new guy got in a fight and Kyle blurted out how he felt. Unsure how to move forward with the new information, the two try this new dynamic out and you won't want to miss how it all goes down.Enjoy!
title: Fell From My Lips
